title: [Boreas Hills, Mistral Court]
description: Homes line the street here, each sitting on its own small plot of land.  Tidy wooden fences surround several of them, ivy growing up and around the slats, giving the whole area a very picturesque look.

Homes line the street here, each sitting on its own small plot of land.  Tidy wooden fences surround several of them, ivy growing up and around the slats.  In addition to the illumination from the moon, several lanterns sit on fence posts here and there.
